<title>USA: Peritus Software IPO range increased.</title>
<headline>Peritus Software IPO range increased.</headline>
<dateline>NEW YORK 1997-06-30</dateline>
<text>
<p>Peritus Software Inc's initial public offering range has been raised to $12 - $14 per share from $10 - $12, said underwriter Montgomery Securities.</p>
<p>The deal is expected to involve the pricing of 2.9 million shares for trade on July 1.</p>
<p>Peritus of Billerica, Mass., develops software to deal with large-scale changes that can trip up other software, such as the changeover to the year 2000 or the European Union's expected conversion to a single currency.</p>
